    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom Hero is a game that combines storage organization and rogue light action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By setting “chips” in storage, the player's stats and possible actions increase according to the effect of the “chip”, enhancing the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize and fight against enemies, and aim to defeat the boss at the lowest level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Chips </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Placing “chips” in storage changes the character's status and increases the number of actions possible. The effect can also be enhanced by enlarging the “chip” itself. There are several types of chips, including actions (attack, evade), status (HP, speed, attack power), and items that can be used up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189100/extras/b617465269d44f46d1b12ac6195e3a4b.poster.avif?t=1744081946\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189100/extras/b617465269d44f46d1b12ac6195e3a4b.webm?t=1744081946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189100/extras/b617465269d44f46d1b12ac6195e3a4b.mp4?t=1744081946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189100/extras/404465c5f12f158b07e4235c01ce410f.poster.avif?t=1744081946\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189100/extras/404465c5f12f158b07e4235c01ce410f.webm?t=1744081946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse